### ============================================================

# @timeout 120000
PATCH {{EcoFleet.API_HostAddress}}/deactivate/B2C3D4E5-F6A7-8901-BCDE-F12345678901

###

### ============================================================
### ACTIVATE ASSIGNMENT
### ============================================================

# @timeout 120000
